Development of active, nanoparticle, antimicrobial technologies for muscle-based 
packaging applications.

Morris MA(1), Padmanabhan SC(2), Cruz-Romero MC(3), Cummins E(4), Kerry JP(5).

Author information:
(1)Advanced Materials and Bioengineering Research (AMBER), School of Chemistry, 
Trinity College Dublin, College Green, Dublin 2, Ireland. Electronic address: 
